{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1152172, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“能做到别人不会的题”也不见得", "timestamp": 1614398202, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152173, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“能把题做明白讲明白”更不一定", "timestamp": 1614398217, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152175, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "教学能力本身是一项和专业能力不完全重合的能力。但是在高学历的人里面筛教学能力强的人、培养教学能力强的人也是一个不错的思路。毕竟学习能力强这件事情，是可以迁移到“学习如何教学”上面来的。", "timestamp": 1614398240, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152179, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然，并不是所有人都能做到这个迁移，所以并不是所有高学历的人都能吃得了高中教师这碗饭", "timestamp": 1614398267, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152216, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同意Bob,教学能力确实是一种不是人人都具备的的专业技能", "timestamp": 1614398664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152228, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得211师范专业的比你清他北半路转行当老师的强多了吧", "timestamp": 1614398798, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 教学能力很多部分是天生的", "timestamp": 1614400022, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152388, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 227812, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得师范学校去当老师的人比清北的基数大，优秀个体也应该更多，个人臆测\n", "timestamp": 1614401152, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 227812, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "#2277